------------------ User Date Script -----------------------

. If u want to add nginx when launching the template of EC2 instance.
. So we have to write the user-data script for that. 

Go to the Launch Template Section --->> Actions --->> Modify Template 
--->> Advanced Section --->> User data - optional 
and write the your shell script for that.

------------- Shell Script

#!/bin/bash

sudo apt-get update -y
sudo apt-get install nginx -y

// This is the command to create the file and write inside them.
sudo echo "aws-learning-session Server IP address is ${hostname -i}" > /var/www/html/index.html

// after that restart nginx
sudo systemctl restart nginx